name: ETHXCPCARD (2015) - Spells Of Genesis
description:
Created by Emblem-Deployer One of the first ever NFTs depicting Ethereum (2015).

Spells Of Genesis are the first-ever blockchain collectibles, game assets and more.

ETHXCPCARD (1/1000) was minted on 9th of August 2015 and details the early battle between the two major token platforms Ethereum (ETH) & Counterparty (XCP).
